tool_description: API that returns the etymological meaning of specified word
title: Etymology Meaning

api_list.name: All Syntaxes
api_list.description: Returns the value for all synataxes available
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://etymology-meaning.p.rapidapi.com/all-syntaxes/{word}"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "etymology-meaning.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())
